		{
			"text": "Security update for the Linux Kernel (Live Patch 24 for SLE 15 SP2)",
			"title": "Topic",
			"type": "Summary"
		},
		{
			"text": "This update for the Linux Kernel 5.3.18-24_102 fixes one issue.\n\nThe following security issue was fixed:\n\n- CVE-2022-0492: Fixed a privilege escalation related to cgroups v1 release_agent feature, which allowed bypassing namespace isolation unexpectedly (bsc#1195543).\n",
			"title": "Details",
			"type": "General"
